-- Changhong, Foxconn Technology to Invest in Flat-Panel Line, Magazine Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-23T23:31:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/changhong-foxconn-technology-to-invest-in-flat-panel-line-magazine-says.html

          
          
             Sichuan Changhong Electric Co. and
Foxconn Technology Group plan to invest in a 27.2 billion yuan
project to build flat-panel production lines with the Chengdu
city government, the China Economy and Informatization magazine
reported, citing an unidentified government official reviewing
the project.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Yu-Huay Sun in Taipei at 
 ysun7@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        